		<Location><X>292</X><Y>8</Y></Location>
		<Size><CX>216</CX><CY>20</CY></Size>
		<TooltipReference>Filter this tradeskill's recipes by name, or type a trivial range like "15-30" to filter by trivial instead.</TooltipReference>
		<Text></Text>
